\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I know what a blade slicing bone feels like.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Shade looks down at his robe, and . He stuck his gloved fingers into it and probed the .}
