\par\pard\plain \sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The first in a line of modest men, with access to a higher truth.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The schism in the modern world is between those who feel that their version of the truth demands that it must be enforced, and those who feel that the only right you have is to make your case to people who are then left alone to agree or not agree.\~}
